## API Calls Made by This Page

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/api/stats` | GET | Metric card totals |
| `/api/users` | GET | Paginated list with search |

Both are called from the Server Component. They use the `Authorization` header read from the cookie via `cookies()`.

