## Design Notes ({{ design_style }})

{% if design_style == "minimal-clean" %}
- Metric cards: white background, 1px border, large number in font-semibold, muted label, subtle trend indicator
- Table: minimal borders (bottom row separator only), ample cell padding, hover row highlight
- Actions: text links rather than icon buttons; reveal on row hover
- Spacing: `p-6` page padding, `gap-6` between sections
{% elif design_style == "corporate-professional" %}
- Metric cards: solid colored top border per category, icon aligned left, number prominent
- Table: full bordered, alternating row backgrounds, header with sort indicators
- Actions: icon button group per row, always visible
- Dense layout: `p-4` padding, tighter `gap-4`
{% elif design_style == "playful-modern" %}
- Metric cards: gradient background per card, rounded-2xl, icon in colored circle
- Table: card-style container with rounded corners, no outer border
- Actions: colored pill badges, animated hover states
- Spacing: `p-8` padding, `gap-8` between sections, extra breathing room
{% endif %}
